sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Sender (WS)
    participant MS1 as MS Server A
    participant Bus as Pub/Sub (workspace)
    participant Per as Persist Svc
    participant MS2 as MS Server B
    participant B as Recipient (WS)

    Note over A,B: Send message in channel -> fan-out to subscribers
    A->>MS1: WS send {channel_id, text}
    MS1->>MS1: auth + rate limit
    MS1-)Per: persist to wide-column (channel partition)
    MS1-)Bus: publish to channel topic
    Per->>Per: write messages table
    Per-)Per: index in ES (async)
    Bus-)MS1: deliver to local subscribers
    Bus-)MS2: deliver to remote MS server
    MS2-)B: WS push message
    MS1-->>A: ack {message_ts}
    alt recipient offline OR mention
        Per-)Per: Notif Svc consumes stream
        Note over Per: APNs/FCM push (deduped by user_id, message_ts)
    end
